ponses on the basis of topographic projections between the IC and auditory cortex. However, corticofugal modulation of collicular amplitude sensitivity is primarily dependent upon the difference but not the absolute amplitude sensitivity between collicular and cortical neurons.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Jen, Philip H.-S.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Zhou, Xiaoming", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/3e0b1267bb737695c5ac619ef09c444a", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/d2544094b0c9a232b8c5e3d0672915aba7f9db553300cea5d90995253fc5cef3", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/H9W98PBK", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/H9W98PBK", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/d7f1a11e7de2176874076f8c9d531dda!/b34481-36941", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "1-2", "pages": "91-106", "title": "Hearing Research", "volume": "184"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/3e0b1267bb737695c5ac619ef09c444a"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:H9W98PBK"}, {"identifier": "10.1016/S0378-5955(03)00237-5"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "i